00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:40,720
Meimei!

5
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:41,980
Dad!

6
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:42,880
My baby!

7
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,960
I miss you so much!

8
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:49,560
Do you miss daddy?

9
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,160
Yes, I do.

10
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:54,880
Where's your mom?

11
