I'm just tired

12
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,000
and want to take a break for sometime.

13
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:00,960
For who?

14
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,430
Why don't just give it to us?

15
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,030
Right?

16
00:02:04,270 --> 00:02:05,080
When you make money

17
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:06,390
give me some bonus.

18
00:02:07,190 --> 00:02:08,090
Alright.

19
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:11,460
Darling, you're back.

20
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,180
Honey.

21
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:13,460
Tired, I guess.

22
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,530
- It's fine.
- Get some rest.

23
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:16,900
Honey.

24
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,240
Where's your stuff?

25
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,060
Why are they all gone?

26
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,770
I quit.

27
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,530
Why?

28
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,060
What do you mean why?

29
00:02:25,670 --> 00:02:26,580
There's a stop-loss

30
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:27,860
in stock trading, right?

31
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:28,930
I've thought about it.

32
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:30,650
I'm going to get a job.

33
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:33,340
Watching the shop downstairs
or something.

34
00:02:34,270 --> 00:02:36,300
There's less money,
but there's also less work.

35
00:02:36,990 --> 00:02:38,530
It doesn't stop me
from picking up the kid.

36
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,090
Right, baby?

37
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:41,620
But...

38
00:02:41,830 --> 00:02:42,530
Honey.

39
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:44,530
I, uhm...

40
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,810
You've been fired, right?

41
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:48,300
It's fine.

42
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,210
We're all on this together.

43
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,620
Thank you, honey.

44
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:54,900
Thanks.

45
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,210
Thank you.

46
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,240
But I'm fine here.

47
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,380
No suspension.

48
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,060
Everything will be fine.

49
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,340
What?

50
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,420
The patient's not dead?

51
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:08,440
No, patient's alive.

52
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,370
Don't you have to resign?

53
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:10,970
No.

54
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,090
It's just that...

55
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,300
In the meantime, I've got to work over...

56
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,180
Sisters.

57
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:16,900
The stuff!

58
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:18,370
Return it to me!

59
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,300
I'm not tired now!

60
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:20,810
Daddy.

61
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,180
What's this?

62
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,530
This is

63
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,770
my invitation.

64
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,090
Dad's about to join

65
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:28,280
Dr. Zheng's team.

66
00:03:28,830 --> 00:03:30,420
It's just that when I'm busy,

67
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,250
I may not have time to spend with you.

68
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:33,140
It's okay, Daddy.

69
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:34,970
You're the best doctor ever.

70
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,490
Thanks, baby.

71
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,300
Meimei is the best.

72
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:49,500
[Episode 21]

73
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,300
[United We Stand, Earthquake Relief]

74
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,020
He is joining us.

75
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,060
That's great.

76
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,650
But

77
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,930
the technical problem has not
been solved yet.

78
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,300
We need an extracardiac surgeon.

79
00:04:17,350 --> 00:04:18,010
Su Yun.

80
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:20,450
About the live streaming...

81
00:04:21,150 --> 00:04:22,010
I'm not ready yet.

82
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:29,010
Dear Zheng.

83
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,540
You seem to be

84
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,860
full of energy today, too.

85
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:35,000
It's already dark

86
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,810
and you're just here.

87
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:38,060
I'm here to pick up
my dear Yue from work.

88
00:04:38,350 --> 00:04:39,180
What?

89
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,860
It's a secret between me and Yue.

90
00:04:43,230 --> 00:04:44,180
It doesn't concern you.

91
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,250
Dear Yue!

92
00:04:47,710 --> 00:04:48,980
Dear Rudolph.

93
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:50,130
The conjoined twins will be transferred.

94
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,560
[Duty Room
Communication Room]

95
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,300
Dr. Chang.

96
00:04:56,150 --> 00:04:56,980
Dr. Zheng.

97
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,930
Over the time,

98
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,980
I know you've done

99
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:02,890
a lot for the twin sisters.

100
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,060
But this opportunity

101
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,370
is truly rare.

102
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,890
If we missed it

103
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,570
we would always be reminded later

104
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:10,930
in the frustration, heartache

105
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,180
of caring for our children.

106
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,490
Reminded it would've been better

107
00:05:13,710 --> 00:05:15,810
if we'd gone
to Women and Children's Hospital.

108
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,540
We don't want to have any regrets.

109
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:24,980
Go ahead.

110
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:28,980
You...

111
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,740
Do you really agree?

112
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,010
500.

113
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:35,620
Think about it before you decide.

114
00:05:42,030 --> 00:05:42,860
Frankly,

115
00:05:45,150 --> 00:05:46,250
I haven't come up

116
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,540
with a better solution so far.

117
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:50,180
I'm not very confident
about this surgery.

118
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:53,620
You deserve a better hospital

119
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,740
and don't feel guilty about it.

120
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:58,420
Go.

121
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:04,010
Thanks.

122
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,010
I'm sorry.

123
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:07,690
Thank you.

124
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:09,740
Sorry.

125
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:18,660
[Haicheng Hospital]

126
00:06:20,910 --> 00:06:22,420
After all this effort, why?

127
00:06:24,590 --> 00:06:26,010
The Women and Children's Hospital
is interested

128
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:27,080
in this case

129
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,740
as a demonstration surgery.

130
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:30,250
They'll do it all for free.

131
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,330
It's too tempting.

132
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,570
I didn't expect that.

133
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,660
Yeah.

134
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,300
Didn't expect Women & Children's Hospital
to come in at the last minute.

135
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,250
I mean, I didn't expect

136
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:38,690
Zheng Ren to be so gentle.

137
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,100
I thought he'd be

138
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:41,490
dead set on the surgery.

139
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,570
Treatment

140
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:49,810
is sometimes not only

141
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,180
for the patient

142
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,540
but also for the family.

143
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:55,010
In this case of conjoined twins,

144
00:06:55,150 --> 00:06:56,890
it's not just the twin sisters

145
00:06:56,910 --> 00:06:58,620
who really need to live,

146
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,180
it's the parents who count on them

147
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:04,130
to continue their normal lives.

148
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:05,540
That's why

149
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,490
Dr. Zheng let go, right?

150
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,660
Zheng.

151
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,930
The conjoined twins surgery is out.

152
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,060
[Letter of Appointment]
Let's go to Germany.

153
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,320
I've got a contract.

154
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,490
Check it out.

155
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,490
Take a look.

156
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,490
I'm not going.

157
00:07:35,910 --> 00:07:36,740
Why?

158
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,220
Why won't you go?

159
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:41,890
Heart failure.

160
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:44,980
What happened?

161
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,330
The most important issue
for the conjoined twins

162
00:07:46,330 --> 00:07:47,130
is preventing heart failure.

163
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,660
I forgot to remind them earlier.

164
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,740
The family's already gone.

165
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,860
Tell them by phone

166
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,220
to avoid awkwardness.

167
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:15,300
There's an earthquake in Nanyang Town.

168
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,540
Ms. Su wants us all

169
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,660
to gather in the auditorium.

170
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:22,080
[Magnitude 7.1 earthquake
hit Nanyang Town, Peicheng, Hexi]

171
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,980
CENC officially determined

172
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,780
that at 19:30 today,

173
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,330
Nanyang Town, Peicheng, Hexi,

174
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:29,010
was hit by a 7.1 magnitude earthquake.

175
00:08:29,010 --> 00:08:29,890
Tremors are strongly felt.

176
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,620
Heavy damage
to communications base stations.

177
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,930
The impact on the local population

178
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:35,210
and people in the surrounding areas
has been considerable.

179
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,780
Currently, the communications station

180
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:38,810
is severely damaged
and communications are down.

181
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:41,020
Specific casualties
and situations unknown.

182
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,500
After the earthquake,

183
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:43,660
the provincial government

184
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:45,690
and the municipal government leaders

185
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,800
are to give instructions.

186
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,850
Haicheng relevant leaders

187
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,210
led the relevant municipal departments

188
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,280
rush to Peicheng

189
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:52,330
Earthquake Relief Command for guidance.

190
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,260
Top leaders of county councils

191
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:55,850
hurried to the Dongyuan township

192
00:08:55,990 --> 00:08:57,230
Earthquake Relief headquarters

193
00:08:57,230 --> 00:08:59,260
to schedule earthquake relief work.

194
00:09:04,830 --> 00:09:06,380
We've all seen the news.

195
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:09,380
There's been an earthquake in Hexi area

196
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:11,020
and needs urgent support.

197
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,690
While getting the supplies ready,

198
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,690
I'll say a few words.

199
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,090
You all know

200
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,730
the symbol of Haicheng

201
00:09:21,110 --> 00:09:22,300
is a tent.

202
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:25,300
Our three founders met as a result

203
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,420
of a rescue operation during

204
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,610
the great floods

205
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,260
twenty years ago.

206
00:09:33,110 --> 00:09:33,810
Natural calamities.

207
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,970
A huge natural calamities.

208
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:39,450
But counting the three great floods
of this century.

209
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:41,180
Year 1931,

210
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:43,660
145,000 deaths.

211
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,090
Year 1954,

212
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:47,020
33,000 deaths.

213
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:49,060
In their case,

214
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:52,330
it was reduced to 4,150 deaths.

215
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,610
Why?

216
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:56,690
In addition to easy access

217
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:58,060
well-developed communications,

218
00:09:58,470 --> 00:09:59,380
timely command

219
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,850
and professional rescue,

220
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:01,780
there were

221
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:03,970
medical advances.

222
00:10:05,350 --> 00:10:07,500
The injured were treated
at the first opportunity.

223
00:10:08,110 --> 00:10:09,900
Keeping the epidemic firmly

224
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,260
in place.

225
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,730
Modern medicine

226
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:16,060
has allowed us humans

227
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,570
to finally say "we can save them"

228
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,850
to natural disasters.

229
00:10:32,350 --> 00:10:32,930
Everyone.

230
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:39,990
Now is the moment

231
00:10:39,990 --> 00:10:41,570
you can say that now.

232
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,180
For this Hexi earthquake,

233
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,300
any of you can voluntarily sign up.

234
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,810
We'll get ready to go.

235
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:04,720
Let's volunteer.

236
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,400
They need us.

237
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:10,380
Yeah.

238
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,060
We have to go.

239
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:14,900
I'll go.

240
00:11:21,470 --> 00:11:22,420
Our team is going.

241
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,180
We'll go.

242
00:11:23,990 --> 00:11:24,660
I'll go too.

243
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,090
I'll go.

244
00:11:26,170 --> 00:11:26,930
I'll go too.

245
00:11:27,230 --> 00:11:31,690
- I'll go too.
- I'll go.

246
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:32,810
- We're all going.
- I will go.

247
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:34,450
- I'll join.
- Me too.

248
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,660
- And me.
- And me.

249
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:57,920
CENC officially determined that

250
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,660
at 19:30 today,...

