[Magnitude 7.1 earthquake
hit Nanyang Town, Peicheng, Hexi]

252
00:12:00,710 --> 00:12:02,140
Did you get in touch with
Dongyuan Township Hospital?

253
00:12:02,350 --> 00:12:03,180
Not yet.

254
00:12:03,830 --> 00:12:04,810
Keep trying.

255
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:05,540
Yes.

256
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,000
How many supplies do we have left

257
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,970
in our warehouse in Haicheng?

258
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:09,330
How many cars can we arrange?

259
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:10,920
Tents, mineral water,

260
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,300
quilts, cotton clothing, etc.

261
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,090
Around 27 light trucks can be loaded.

262
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,520
And then there's an emergency shipment

263
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,230
of first aid medicines.

264
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:17,260
Cars are divided to three shifts.

265
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:18,850
Latest by tomorrow morning.

266
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:19,660
Got it.

267
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,450
Inform the first car

268
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,570
to get ready in 30 minutes.

269
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,260
Follow me to Dongyuan township.

270
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:25,060
Understood.

271
00:12:26,990 --> 00:12:27,660
Dad.

272
