[Haicheng Hospital]

275
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,340
Be careful.

276
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:45,800
[Earthquake relief]

277
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:46,810
Be safe on the road.

278
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:47,530
Keep in contact.

279
00:12:47,530 --> 00:12:48,240
Don't worry.

280
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,280
Stay safe.

281
