- Go back.

282
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,300
- Bye.
- Stay safe on the road.

283
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,330
- I'm leaving.
- Goodbye.

284
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:55,280
- Be careful.
- Goodbye, president.

285
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,240
- Good luck.
- See you.

