I'll be back.

293
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,210
That kid!

294
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:37,860
[Good night! My little cactus]

295
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:42,860
What are you doing?

296
00:13:43,110 --> 00:13:44,030
Writing a will?

297
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:46,280
Yun.

298
00:13:46,990 --> 00:13:48,540
You're actually a nice guy,

299
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:51,210
but sometimes you talk a little mean.

300
00:13:53,870 --> 00:13:54,780
Lend me a sheet of paper.

301
00:14:02,590 --> 00:14:03,610
You're not writing anything?

302
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:05,690
No one will receive it.

303
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,210
It's actually fine not to write it.

304
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:11,420
If you live, you can do anything.

305
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,140
If I die,

306
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,260
even though Hua is always mean to me,

307
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,500
she'll be crying
with the note in her arms.

308
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:18,660
Saying she miss me.

309
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:21,300
Stop writing.

310
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:33,850
It's my choice.

311
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,850
I'll take all responsibility.

312
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:40,410
I can't rely on you guys to keep me

313
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:41,690
out of trouble forever.

314
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:47,970
Just listen to me for once.

315
00:14:48,110 --> 00:14:49,330
Just respect me for once.

316
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:05,930
Dad.

317
00:15:18,230 --> 00:15:18,780
Dad.

318
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:21,540
I'll be back.

319
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:48,850
Oh, no!

320
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,020
- This is bad!
- What?

321
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:51,610
I didn't take my charm.

322
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,870
It was in your locker last time.

323
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:54,060
Charm?

324
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,930
Why is it in my locker?

325
00:15:56,110 --> 00:15:57,120
Last time, I was in a hurry

326
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,540
and put it in your locker.

327
00:15:58,710 --> 00:16:00,040
Go get it for me.

328
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:01,450
I don't have the keys. You go.

329
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,810
Driver, close the door.

330
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:07,260
Write your thing.

331
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:24,500
[Expert medical team
for earthquake relief]

332
00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:39,780
♪Scattered in the wind,
never mentioned by anyone again...♪

333
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:43,610
He lied to you.

334
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:47,930
Just you wait, Su Yun.

335
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:49,500
Stay with us.

336
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,520
I need you too.

337
00:16:56,300 --> 00:17:02,900
♪Learning to heal
but never soothe the pain♪

338
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:10,900
♪The loneliest scenery
soaked in the rain♪

339
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:18,380
♪The winter gradually warming,
gradually departing♪

340
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:25,580
♪You and I share the same temperament♪

341
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:26,820
[Haicheng Hospital]

342
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:32,100
♪Unrestrained and free-spirited,
as if never accepting fate♪

343
00:18:44,980 --> 00:18:47,380
[Infinite Horizons in Medicine]

344
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:12,060
[Medical team for earthquake relief]

345
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,200
Come on! Let's get this load off.

346
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,470
- Come and unload the car.
- Coming.

347
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,780
Give me a hand here.

348
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:18,940
On my way.

349
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,260
Get some more people over here.

350
00:19:20,410 --> 00:19:21,240
- Alright.
- I'm coming.

351
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:24,410
Move forward.

352
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:28,540
- There's another car up ahead.
- Coming!

353
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:29,810
I'm commander of the 13th Battalion.

354
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,410
My name is Zhao.

355
00:19:30,550 --> 00:19:31,740
The road ahead is blocked

356
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:32,810
by landslide.

357
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:34,370
We'll have to go around it on foot.

358
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:35,890
Everyone organize the necessary items.

359
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:36,970
- There's a landslide.
- Get out of the car.

360
00:19:36,970 --> 00:19:37,470
Come out from the car.

361
00:19:37,470 --> 00:19:38,330
Alright.

362
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:40,010
Stay safe.

363
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,300
Everybody be careful.

364
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,810
Take care of your stuff.

365
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:49,370
Follow me. Go forward.

366
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,730
Let's go forward.

367
00:19:53,130 --> 00:19:54,540
Grab your stuff and go.

368
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:55,400
Pay attention to personal safety

369
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:00,080
This way.

370
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,920
Get your stuff and move forward.

371
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,630
Keep up.

372
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:07,230
Stay with me.

373
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:08,090
Be careful.

374
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,370
[Nanyang town border]
There's a kid over there!

375
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:54,610
On my way!

376
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,610
Hurry!

377
00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:56,780
Come on, two more people!

378
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:58,060
Coming!

379
00:20:59,550 --> 00:21:00,350
- Help!
- There's a movement!

380
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:01,240
Dig this way.

381
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:03,360
Come.

382
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:04,260
Dig down.

383
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,610
Help me!

384
00:21:09,690 --> 00:21:10,810
I've got someone here!

385
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:11,900
Here, give me your hand!

386
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,570
Mom!

387
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:15,340
Somebody!

388
00:21:15,340 --> 00:21:17,460
Please save my mom!

389
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:20,620
I'm begging you, save my mom!

390
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:21,440
Save my mom!

391
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,670
Put it on. Don't worry.

392
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:29,810
Careful.

393
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:54,360
Three, two, one!

394
00:21:59,210 --> 00:22:00,400
It's stuck.

395
00:22:11,130 --> 00:22:12,350
Come on, dig.

396
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:19,310
Miss, are you a doctor?

397
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,800
Save my mom!

398
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:21,330
Alright.

399
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:22,170
Take me to your mom.

400
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,030
Dad! Mom!

401
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:36,000
- Somebody help!
- Save my mom!

402
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,770
She's still in there! Help her!

403
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:38,670
Somebody help me!

404
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,700
You can't go in!

405
00:22:39,700 --> 00:22:40,570
You can't go in there!

406
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:42,160
- It's dangerous in there!
- It's too dangerous!

407
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,130
It's dangerous inside!

408
00:22:43,150 --> 00:22:44,280
- You must save her!
- Zheng Ren!

409
00:22:44,510 --> 00:22:45,440
It's alright!

410
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:47,820
54.

411
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:48,600
55.

412
00:22:48,780 --> 00:22:49,690
56.

413
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,830
57.

414
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:51,720
58.

415
00:22:52,790 --> 00:22:53,500
Have a break.

416
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:54,250
We'll do it.

417
00:22:56,470 --> 00:22:58,280
65! 66!

418
00:22:58,280 --> 00:23:00,280
67! 68!

419
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:01,290
- 69!
- I'm sorry.

420
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,760
Thanks for your work.

421
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:10,260
He just saved several people.

422
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:13,130
But no one could save him.

423
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:14,380
Jin Yaowu?

424
00:23:18,970 --> 00:23:20,010
Which one of you is leading the team?

425
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:21,370
Mr. Kong.

426
00:23:22,430 --> 00:23:23,850
Did you guys come with supplies?

427
00:23:23,990 --> 00:23:25,080
The road collapsed and the car stopped.

428
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:26,110
That's all we can carry.

429
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,060
Fine.

430
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:28,610
Better than nothing.

431
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,300
Come with me.

432
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:31,210
Let's go.

433
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:32,080
Stretcher!

434
00:23:32,120 --> 00:23:33,240
- This way.
- On my way!

435
00:23:46,230 --> 00:23:46,980
Mum!

436
00:23:46,990 --> 00:23:48,890
I got a doctor to help you.

437
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,060
Miss!

438
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:51,610
Save my mom.

439
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,500
I'm sorry.

440
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:15,260
It's okay.

441
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:28,990
Somebody, please!

442
00:24:28,990 --> 00:24:30,110
It's raining!

443
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:40,430
Is there any more gauze?

444
00:24:40,940 --> 00:24:42,240
Did you make the call?

445
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,300
When will the helicopter arrive?

446
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:44,130
I just got off the phone.

447
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:44,890
Because it's raining,

448
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,810
the fog is blocking the view.

449
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:46,850
- The visibility is very low.
- Mr. Kong!

450
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:48,260
Zheng Ren and the team is here.

451
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:48,980
They brought supplies too.

452
00:24:49,030 --> 00:24:50,330
That's great. Let's share it.

453
00:24:50,330 --> 00:24:50,810
Quickly.

454
00:24:50,810 --> 00:24:51,260
Alright.

455
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:52,610
This one's dying.

456
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:55,020
Is there any anaesthetic?

457
00:24:55,120 --> 00:24:55,840
Go over there and take a look.

458
00:24:55,870 --> 00:24:56,480
Alright.

459
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,800
- Ruptured spleen. We have to operate.
- Found it.

460
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:00,880
Surgery?

461
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,940
There's only local anesthesia.

462
00:25:01,950 --> 00:25:03,050
There was no anaesthesia

463
00:25:03,050 --> 00:25:03,940
in the earliest days of surgery.

464
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:05,820
Sterilize sheet, please.

465
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,460
Alright.

466
00:25:10,780 --> 00:25:12,250
It hurts so much!

467
00:25:12,910 --> 00:25:14,190
Hang in there!

468
00:25:14,190 --> 00:25:14,750
Right side.

469
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:16,990
Coming in!

470
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,200
Alright.

471
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:26,510
Done.

472
00:25:26,590 --> 00:25:28,090
Just hang on.

473
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:29,740
That's good.

474
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:32,200
Here, and here.

475
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,120
Just hang in there!

476
00:25:40,220 --> 00:25:41,260
Is there any gauze left?

477
00:25:41,260 --> 00:25:42,460
Give me the haemostat.

478
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:43,240
There's more.

479
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:43,820
Here.

480
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,410
Hang on.

481
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,460
Bear with it!

482
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:54,490
It's almost done.

483
00:25:55,390 --> 00:25:56,250
Anesthetic.

484
00:25:56,250 --> 00:25:57,450
Come on. It'll just take a second.

485
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:58,160
Close it.

486
00:25:58,230 --> 00:25:58,810
Leave it to me.

487
00:25:59,130 --> 00:25:59,920
Wrap it quickly.

488
00:26:02,220 --> 00:26:02,940
Alright.

489
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:04,140
Just a little longer.

490
00:26:04,140 --> 00:26:04,920
Almost there.

491
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:07,480
This way. Hold on.

492
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,080
Alright.

493
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,990
- Writing medical records at this hour?
- Gauze.

494
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:12,010
- It'll come in handy.
- Quickly.

495
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,300
Next.

496
00:26:19,140 --> 00:26:20,820
[Haicheng Hospital]

497
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:21,950
The people has formed

498
00:26:21,950 --> 00:26:23,260
an elite team.

499
00:26:23,710 --> 00:26:25,170
According to the routes assigned

500
00:26:25,170 --> 00:26:26,220
and arranged by the Command Centre,

501
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,850
referring to pre-earthquake maps

502
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:29,460
and maps of administrative areas,

503
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:31,090
they're searching for the village.

504
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:33,060
Using GPS to locate

505
00:26:33,230 --> 00:26:34,940
and bring out all villagers

506
00:26:34,990 --> 00:26:36,130
who can be guided and taken away.

507
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:38,130
[Nanyang Town, Peicheng, Hexi]
Those in camouflage are soldiers.

508
00:26:38,230 --> 00:26:40,220
[Hit by 7.1 magnitude earthquake]
White shirt, blue hat are the paramedics.

509
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,570
There were also

510
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:42,470
many volunteers

511
00:26:42,470 --> 00:26:43,890
in red vests.

512
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,300
They are the spark of hope that spreads

513
00:26:46,710 --> 00:26:49,220
and lights up the mountains.

514
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:59,980
[Zheng Ren]
Be safe and come back safely.

515
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:41,940
Major Gao, you've worked hard.

516
00:27:41,940 --> 00:27:43,020
How's the rescue going so far?

517
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:44,120
We have

518
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:44,890
122 wounded here.

519
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,410
They've all had emergency treatment.

520
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:47,890
But there are 24 seriously injured

521
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:49,060
who need further treatment.

522
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:50,540
We've got a lot of supplies on the way.

523
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,890
You must hold on.

524
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:53,170
Major Gao.

525
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:54,780
Here.

526
00:27:57,070 --> 00:27:58,170
Patient 12,

527
00:27:58,190 --> 00:27:59,980
liver rupture, multiple fractures

528
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:01,870
and hepatic contusion.

529
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:04,410
We'll need a lot of nephrologists
in a few days.

530
00:28:04,470 --> 00:28:05,990
We'll need a lot of dialysis machines.

531
00:28:05,990 --> 00:28:07,530
Redeploy the machine
in the country quickly.

532
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:09,200
What does this mean?

533
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:10,810
This is the record I wrote
for each patient.

534
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:12,850
They are numbered accordingly

535
00:28:13,230 --> 00:28:14,170
on the backs of their hands.

536
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:16,330
It will help the doctors
who'll follow up

537
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,370
to understand their conditions.

538
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:27,650
I'll be sure to send the wounded
and their medical records.

539
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:29,130
By the way.

540
00:28:29,470 --> 00:28:30,650
When I was flying low,

541
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,030
in the northwest corner, I spotted

542
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:33,630
a building 2,000 meters from here,

543
00:28:33,630 --> 00:28:34,760
with people waving white cloths
and calling for help.

544
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:35,700
You guys go over there
and check it out.

545
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,370
Yes.

546
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:38,940
Let's go.

547
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:39,980
Thanks.

548
00:28:50,230 --> 00:28:50,940
Watch your step.

549
00:28:51,690 --> 00:28:52,270
Alright.

550
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:53,850
Careful.

551
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:55,780
Be safe, everyone.

552
00:28:55,780 --> 00:28:56,310
Okay.

553
00:28:56,310 --> 00:28:57,940
Detect trapped persons.

554
00:28:59,270 --> 00:29:00,020
Anyone?

555
00:29:00,070 --> 00:29:00,810
This is a hospital.

556
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:02,600
Hello? Answer me if you hear me.

557
00:29:02,600 --> 00:29:03,320
Anybody?

558
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:04,780
Anyone else here?

559
00:29:05,070 --> 00:29:06,140
- Help!
- Hello?

560
00:29:06,140 --> 00:29:07,440
Is there anyone else?

561
00:29:07,790 --> 00:29:08,810
Help!

562
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:09,500
Casualty on the left.

563
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:10,410
Split up.

564
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,090
There's someone here.

565
00:29:11,120 --> 00:29:11,870
There's more ahead.

566
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,960
- Quick!
- Let's go!

567
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:13,930
Come on!

568
00:29:13,930 --> 00:29:15,180
Quick! Give me a hand.

569
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:16,140
Slowly.

570
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:16,840
Legs are hurt.

571
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:18,090
Slowly! Come on! Harder!

572
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,370
One! Two! Three!

573
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:21,850
One! Two! Three!

574
00:29:21,850 --> 00:29:23,260
Get the wounded out of there.

575
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:24,410
Quickly!

576
00:29:27,470 --> 00:29:28,650
Get the wounded out of here now!

577
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:30,850
Three! Two! One!

578
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,140
Legs!

579
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:35,150
Doctor.

580
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:36,090
What's his condition?

581
00:29:36,090 --> 00:29:36,850
He broke his leg.

582
00:29:36,990 --> 00:29:38,330
Get him back to camp right away.

583
00:29:38,330 --> 00:29:39,610
