589
00:29:44,940 --> 00:29:45,600
Quick!

590
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,830
Su Yun, follow me.

591
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:47,480
Carry away!

592
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:48,220
Come and help.

593
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:50,400
Come with me, two of you.

594
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:56,850
You three go over there.

595
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:57,940
The rest of you, follow me.

596
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:58,740
Yes!

597
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,090
Anyone?

598
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,130
