599
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,020
Hello?

600
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,330
Someone here?

601
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:22,560
Here.

602
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,780
Hurry up and help Dr Zheng.

603
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,650
He's dead.

604
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,170
Carry him away.

605
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:41,740
Did you hear that?

606
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:42,460
A sound.

607
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:21,020
[Outpatient]

608
00:31:40,360 --> 00:31:41,760
You three go over there.

609
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,090
Stay safe.

610
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:44,220
[Outpatient]

611
00:31:44,230 --> 00:31:45,220
Anyone?

612
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:49,090
Anybody?

613
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:55,700
Hello?

614
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:03,170
Is someone there?

615
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:08,700
Answer if you hear me.

616
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:11,940
Watch the top of your head.

617
00:32:14,680 --> 00:32:15,460
Hello?

618
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:23,460
I heard it.

619
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:25,130
There's a kid crying up ahead.

620
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:29,940
Aftershock.

621
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:30,780
Find cover.

622
00:32:42,220 --> 00:32:45,740
[Comprehensive No. 1 ward]

623
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:48,180
[Nanyang Town]

624
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:13,470
Aftershock! It's dangerous.

625
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:14,330
Go!

626
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,760
Su Yun!

627
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:26,800
Run!

628
00:33:26,840 --> 00:33:29,020
- Run away!
- Go! It's dangerous!

629
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:13,170
Su Yun!

630
00:34:13,240 --> 00:34:15,630
Call for reinforcements! Quick!

631
00:34:15,720 --> 00:34:16,170
Yes!

632
00:34:16,190 --> 00:34:16,650
Quick!

633
00:36:58,150 --> 00:36:59,200
Zheng Ren!

634
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,690
Can you hear me?

635
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,540
Mom!

636
00:39:10,190 --> 00:39:11,250
Mom!

637
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,820
Mom!

638
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:15,790
Who's there?

639
00:39:15,790 --> 00:39:16,890
Mom!

640
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:17,940
Where are you?

641
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:19,370
I'm here.

642
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,650
Don't be afraid, little one.

643
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:23,610
I'm a doctor.

644
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:25,860
How are you? Are you okay?

645
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:28,540
Please save my mom!

646
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,980
Alright.

647
00:39:31,550 --> 00:39:32,540
Mom!

648
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,730
Hey, kid.

649
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:35,460
Don't cry.

650
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:36,960
I'll check your mom's body first.

651
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:37,730
Okay.

652
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,900
Mom!

653
00:39:53,630 --> 00:39:54,900
Mom!

654
00:39:55,470 --> 00:39:56,500
Mom!

655
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:08,570
Left calf is fractured.

656
00:40:09,510 --> 00:40:10,500
Haemorrhagic necrosis.

657
00:40:10,920 --> 00:40:12,420
Is mom going to die?

658
00:40:16,670 --> 00:40:18,770
It's my fault for being so slow.

659
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:21,020
Mom got crushed

660
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,290
when trying to save me.

661
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:26,730
Mom!

662
00:40:28,510 --> 00:40:31,210
Mom!

663
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:33,170
Kid.

664
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,020
Don't cry.

665
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,060
Have a drink.

666
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:39,250
I don't want it. Give it to mom.

667
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,500
What's your name?

668
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,060
My name is Bai Yang.

669
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:42,900
Bai Yang.

670
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:44,250
Don't be scared.

671
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,130
Someone will help us later.

672
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:46,980
Alright.

673
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,090
Mom!

674
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:51,340
Zheng Ren!

675
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,290
Commander Zhao!

676
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,860
Can you guys hear me?

677
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,690
Move the light stuff out first.

678
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:02,650
Su Yun!

679
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,170
Please answer when you hear me!

680
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:05,420
Su Yun!

681
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,380
Zheng Ren! What are you doing?

682
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:12,980
