Let go!

683
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,060
Don't you want your hands anymore?

684
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:15,820
Don't you want your hands anymore?

685
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:19,860
Take these gloves on.

