689
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,380
Mom!

690
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:52,690
Mom! Don't leave me!

691
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:54,690
Mom!

692
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,060
Mister!

693
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,640
Aren't you a doctor?

694
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:59,420
You have to save my mom!

695
00:42:00,510 --> 00:42:01,420
Mister!

696
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,090
Oh no.

697
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,340
Mom!

698
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:13,020
Mister, please save my mom!

699
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,980
Save my mom!

700
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:19,570
Mister.

